org.apache.poi.hwpf.model

Class PicturesTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hwpf.model.PicturesTable

  • @Internal
public final class PicturesTable
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds information about all pictures embedded in Word Document either via "Insert -> Picture -> From File" or via clipboard. Responsible for images extraction and determining whether some document's piece contains embedded image. Analyzes raw data bytestream 'Data' (where Word stores all embedded objects) provided by HWPFDocument. Word stores images as is within so called "Data stream" - the stream within a Word docfile containing various data that hang off of characters in the main stream. For example, binary data describing in-line pictures and/or formfields an also embedded objects-native data. Word picture structures are concatenated one after the other in the data stream if the document contains pictures. Data stream is easily reachable via HWPFDocument._dataStream property. A picture is represented in the document text stream as a special character, an Unicode  whose CharacterRun.isSpecial() returns true. The file location of the picture in the Word binary file is accessed via CharacterRun.getPicOffset(). The CharacterRun.getPicOffset() is a byte offset into the data stream. Beginning at the position recorded in picOffset, a header data structure, will be stored.(通过“插入->图片->来自文件”或通过剪贴板保存有关嵌入在Word文档中的所有图片的信息。负责图像提取并确定某文档是否包含嵌入图像。分析HWPFDocument提供的原始数据字节流“Data”（Word存储所有嵌入式对象）。Word将图像存储为所谓的“数据流”中，即Word文档文件中的流，包含主流中字符挂起的各种数据。例如，描述内联图片和/或表格字段的二进制数据也是嵌入对象原生数据。如果文档包含图片，则Word图片结构在数据流中将一个接一个地级联。数据流可以通过HWPFDocument轻松访问。_ dataStream属性。图片在文档文本流中表示为特殊字符（Unicode）  其DeliverRun.isSpecial（）返回true。Word二进制文件中图片的文件位置通过DeliverRun.getPicOffset（）访问。DeliverRun.getPicOffset（）是数据流中的字节偏置。从picOffset中记录的位置开始，将存储头部数据结构。)
    Author:
    Dmitry Romanov

      • extractPicture

        public Picture extractPicture(CharacterRun run,
                              boolean fillBytes)
        Returns picture object tied to specified CharacterRun(返回绑定到指定ButterRun的图片对象)
        Parameters:
        run -(跑-)
        fillBytes - if true, Picture will be returned with filled byte array that represent picture's contents. If you don't want to have that byte array in memory but only write picture's contents to stream, pass false and then use Picture.writeImageContent(fillspel-如果为真，则Picture将返回并包含表示图片内容的已填充字节数组。如果您不想在内存中拥有该字节数组，而只将图片的内容写入流，请传递true，然后使用Picture. writeMediaContent)
        Returns:
        a Picture object if picture exists for specified CharacterRun, null otherwise. PicturesTable.hasPicture is used to determine this.(如果指定的ButterRun存在图片，则为Picture对象，否则为空。PicturesTable.hasPicture用于确定这一点。)
        See Also:
        Picture.writeImageContent(java.io.OutputStream), hasPicture(org.apache.poi.hwpf.usermodel.CharacterRun)

      • getAllPictures

        public java.util.List<Picture> getAllPictures()
        Not all documents have all the images concatenated in the data stream although MS claims so. The best approach is to scan all character runs.(并非所有的文件都在数据流中连接了所有的图像，尽管微软声称如此。最好的方法是扫描所有字符串。)
        Returns:
        a list of Picture objects found in current document(在当前文档中找到的图片对象的列表)
